| Effect | Dependencies | Mutates State? |
|--------|-------------|----------------|
| `useEffect([requestParameterization])` | Stable `useCallback([])` | Indirectly (Zustand store) |
| `useScreenViewTracking` internal `useEffect([isFocused])` | Boolean primitive | No |
